=Description=

"PyraPOD is an open-source, revolutionary food-growing ecosystem that empowers families to produce fresh, local food year-round. Built on smart design, blockchain-backed funding, and a circular economy model, it invites continuous improvement from its user community. PyraPOD is more than a greenhouse — it’s a blueprint for resilience, co-developed and supported by distributed, community-based, worker-owned manufacturing and service hubs. Starting in Windsor, these hubs are designed to scale virally across communities worldwide. An open-source social network will connect end users fostering a cooperative, co-competitive ecosystem for sustainable abundance.

...

Through blockchain-backed smart contracts, investors fund PyraPOD units for families in need. As each greenhouse produces value, both sides benefit: families gain food security and independence, while investors earn returns from real-world assets."


